beer.beer_description:
Brother Boatrocker's Beer.

Tripel is a beer built on the love of Belgian ales... Using our homemade candi syrup, classic Euro malts, delicate spicing and a strain of yeast from Westmalle Abbey results in a balanced strong ale.

Served chilled and pour into a goblet.
